   "source": [
    "## 3. Pra-pemrosesan Data <a name=\"preprocessing\"></a>\n",
    "\n",
    "Sekarang, mari pra-proses data untuk pelatihan:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Normalisasi nilai piksel ke rentang [0, 1]\n",
    "x_train = x_train.astype('float32') / 255\n",
    "x_test = x_test.astype('float32') / 255\n",
    "\n",
    "# Ubah bentuk data untuk model dense (meratakan gambar 28x28)\n",
    "x_train_flat = x_train.reshape(-1, 784)\n",
    "x_test_flat = x_test.reshape(-1, 784)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Juga simpan bentuk asli untuk model CNN nanti\n",
    "x_train_cnn = x_train.reshape(-1, 28, 28, 1)\n",
    "x_test_cnn = x_test.reshape(-1, 28, 28, 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Konversi vektor kelas ke matriks kelas biner (one-hot encoding)\n",
    "y_train_cat = to_categorical(y_train, 10)\n",
    "y_test_cat = to_categorical(y_test, 10)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Bentuk data flat setelah pra-pemrosesan: {x_train_flat.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Bentuk data CNN setelah pra-pemrosesan: {x_train_cnn.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Bentuk label setelah one-hot encoding: {y_train_cat.shape}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. Arsitektur Model <a name=\"architecture\"></a>\n",
    "\n",
    "Mari kita definisikan arsitektur model kita. Kita akan pertama-tama mengimplementasikan jaringan dense original, kemudian meningkatkannya dengan CNN."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Buat model Dense original\n",
    "model_dense = Sequential([\n",
    "    Dense(64, activation='relu', input_dim=784),\n",
    "    Dense(64, activation='relu'), \n",
    "    Dense(10, activation='softmax'),\n",
    "])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Kompilasi model\n",
    "model_dense.compile(\n",
    "    optimizer='adam',\n",
    "    loss='categorical_crossentropy',\n",
    "    metrics=['accuracy']\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Ringkasan model\n",
    "model_dense.summary()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Buat model CNN yang ditingkatkan\n",
    "model_cnn = Sequential([\n",
    "    Conv2D(32, kernel_size=(3, 3), activation='relu', input_shape=(28, 28, 1)),\n",
    "    Conv2D(64, (3, 3), activation='relu'),\n",
    "    MaxPooling2D(pool_size=(2, 2)),\n",
    "    Dropout(0.25),\n",
    "    Flatten(),\n",
    "    Dense(128, activation='relu'),\n",
    "    Dropout(0.5),\n",
    "    Dense(10, activation='softmax')\n",
    "])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Kompilasi model\n",
    "model_cnn.compile(\n",
    "    optimizer='adam',\n",
    "    loss='categorical_crossentropy',\n",
    "    metrics=['accuracy']\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Ringkasan model\n",
    "model_cnn.summary()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. Pelatihan Model dengan Visualisasi <a name=\"training\"></a>\n",
    "\n",
    "Mari kita latih kedua model dan visualisasikan proses pelatihan."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Siapkan callbacks untuk pelacakan yang lebih baik\n",
    "callbacks = [\n",
    "    ModelCheckpoint('mnist_best_model.h5', save_best_only=True, monitor='val_accuracy'),\n",
    "    EarlyStopping(monitor='val_loss', patience=3, restore_best_weights=True),\n",
    "    CSVLogger('training_log.csv')\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "# Latih model Dense\n",
    "history_dense = model_dense.fit(\n",
    "    x_train_flat, y_train_cat,\n",
    "    epochs=10,\n",
    "    batch_size=128,\n",
    "    validation_split=0.1,\n",
    "    callbacks=callbacks,\n",
    "    verbose=1\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Latih model CNN\n",
    "history_cnn = model_cnn.fit(\n",
    "    x_train_cnn, y_train_cat,\n",
    "    epochs=10,\n",
    "    batch_size=128,\n",
    "    validation_split=0.1,\n",
    "    callbacks=callbacks,\n",
    "    verbose=1\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Fungsi untuk menampilkan history pelatihan\n",
    "def plot_training_history(history, title):\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 5))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Plot akurasi\n",
    "    plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)\n",
    "    plt.plot(history.history['accuracy'], label='Akurasi Pelatihan')\n",
    "    plt.plot(history.history['val_accuracy'], label='Akurasi Validasi')\n",
    "    plt.title(f'{title} - Akurasi')\n",
    "    plt.xlabel('Epoch')\n",
    "    plt.ylabel('Akurasi')\n",
    "    plt.legend()\n",
    "    plt.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Plot loss\n",
    "    plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)\n",
    "    plt.plot(history.history['loss'], label='Loss Pelatihan')\n",
    "    plt.plot(history.history['val_loss'], label='Loss Validasi')\n",
    "    plt.title(f'{title} - Loss')\n",
    "    plt.xlabel('Epoch')\n",
    "    plt.ylabel('Loss')\n",
    "    plt.legend()\n",
    "    plt.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Tampilkan history pelatihan untuk kedua model\n",
    "plot_training_history(history_dense, 'Model Dense')\n",
    "plot_training_history(history_cnn, 'Model CNN')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. Evaluasi Model <a name=\"evaluation\"></a>\n",
    "\n",
    "Sekarang mari kita evaluasi kedua model pada set pengujian dan bandingkan performanya."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Evaluasi model Dense\n",
    "dense_loss, dense_accuracy = model_dense.evaluate(x_test_flat, y_test_cat)\n",
    "print(f\"Model Dense - Akurasi Pengujian: {dense_accuracy*100:.2f}%\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Evaluasi model CNN\n",
    "cnn_loss, cnn_accuracy = model_cnn.evaluate(x_test_cnn, y_test_cat)\n",
    "print(f\"Model CNN - Akurasi Pengujian: {cnn_accuracy*100:.2f}%\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Fungsi untuk membuat dan memvisualisasikan matriks kebingungan (confusion matrix)\n",
    "def plot_confusion_matrix(model, x_test, y_test, model_name):\n",
    "    # Dapatkan prediksi\n",
    "    y_pred = model.predict(x_test)\n",
    "    y_pred_classes = np.argmax(y_pred, axis=1)\n",
    "    y_true = np.argmax(y_test, axis=1)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Hitung matriks kebingungan\n",
    "    cm = confusion_matrix(y_true, y_pred_classes)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Plot matriks kebingungan\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))\n",
    "    sns.heatmap(cm, annot=True, fmt='d', cmap='Blues', cbar=False)\n",
    "    plt.title(f'{model_name} - Matriks Kebingungan')\n",
    "    plt.ylabel('Label Sebenarnya')\n",
    "    plt.xlabel('Label yang Diprediksi')\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Cetak laporan klasifikasi\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n{model_name} - Laporan Klasifikasi:\")\n",
    "    print(classification_report(y_true, y_pred_classes))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return y_pred, y_pred_classes, y_true\n",
    "\n",
    "# Plot matriks kebingungan untuk kedua model\n",
    "dense_pred, dense_pred_classes, y_true = plot_confusion_matrix(model_dense, x_test_flat, y_test_cat, 'Model Dense')\n",
    "cnn_pred, cnn_pred_classes, _ = plot_confusion_matrix(model_cnn, x_test_cnn, y_test_cat, 'Model CNN')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. Visualisasi Prediksi <a name=\"predictions\"></a>\n",
    "\n",
    "Mari kita visualisasikan beberapa prediksi untuk melihat bagaimana model bekerja pada contoh spesifik."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Fungsi untuk memvisualisasikan prediksi model\n",
    "def visualize_predictions(x_data, y_true, y_pred, model_name, num_samples=10):\n",
    "    # Dapatkan indeks acak\n",
    "    indices = np.random.choice(len(x_data), num_samples, replace=False)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Plot prediksi\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(15, 6))\n",
    "    for i, idx in enumerate(indices):\n",
    "        plt.subplot(2, 5, i+1)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # Ubah bentuk gambar untuk ditampilkan jika diperlukan\n",
    "        if len(x_data.shape) == 2:  # Jika diratakan\n",
    "            img = x_data[idx].reshape(28, 28)\n",
    "        else:  # Jika sudah dalam format 2D atau 3D\n",
    "            img = x_data[idx].reshape(28, 28)\n",
    "            \n",
    "        plt.imshow(img, cmap='gray')\n",
    "        \n",
    "        pred_class = np.argmax(y_pred[idx])\n",
    "        true_class = y_true[idx]\n",
    "        confidence = y_pred[idx][pred_class] * 100\n",
    "        \n",
    "        color = 'green' if pred_class == true_class else 'red'\n",
    "        plt.title(f\"Prediksi: {pred_class}\\nBenar: {true_class}\\nKeyakinan: {confidence:.1f}%\", color=color)\n",
    "        plt.axis('off')\n",
    "        \n",
    "    plt.suptitle(f\"Prediksi {model_name}\", y=1.05, fontsize=16)\n",
    "    plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Visualisasikan prediksi untuk kedua model\n",
    "visualize_predictions(x_test_flat, y_true, dense_pred, 'Model Dense')\n",
    "visualize_predictions(x_test_cnn, y_true, cnn_pred, 'Model CNN')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Temukan dan visualisasikan contoh yang paling menantang (keyakinan terendah)\n",
    "def find_challenging_examples(x_data, y_true, y_pred, model_name, num_samples=10):\n",
    "    # Hitung keyakinan untuk kelas yang benar\n",
    "    confidences = np.array([y_pred[i, true_class] for i, true_class in enumerate(y_true)])\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Temukan indeks dari prediksi dengan keyakinan terendah\n",
    "    hard_indices = np.argsort(confidences)[:num_samples]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(15, 6))\n",
    "    for i, idx in enumerate(hard_indices):\n",
    "        plt.subplot(2, 5, i+1)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # Ubah bentuk gambar untuk ditampilkan jika diperlukan\n",
    "        if len(x_data.shape) == 2:  # Jika diratakan\n",
    "            img = x_data[idx].reshape(28, 28)\n",
    "        else:  # Jika sudah dalam format 2D atau 3D\n",
    "            img = x_data[idx].reshape(28, 28)\n",
    "            \n",
    "        plt.imshow(img, cmap='gray')\n",
    "        \n",
    "        pred_class = np.argmax(y_pred[idx])\n",
    "        true_class = y_true[idx]\n",
    "        confidence = y_pred[idx][true_class] * 100\n",
    "        \n",
    "        color = 'green' if pred_class == true_class else 'red'\n",
    "        plt.title(f\"Prediksi: {pred_class}\\nBenar: {true_class}\\nKeyakinan: {confidence:.1f}%\", color=color)\n",
    "        plt.axis('off')\n",
    "        \n",
    "    plt.suptitle(f\"{model_name} - Contoh Paling Menantang\", y=1.05, fontsize=16)\n",
    "    plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "    \n",
    "# Temukan contoh menantang untuk kedua model\n",
    "find_challenging_examples(x_test_flat, y_true, dense_pred, 'Model Dense')\n",
    "find_challenging_examples(x_test_cnn, y_true, cnn_pred, 'Model CNN')"
   ]
